<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT25">
<l>vakaiyāṉ matiyātu maṇkoṇṭāy maṟṟum</l>
<l>vakaiyāṉ varuvatoṉ ṟuṇṭē vakaiyāl</l>
<l>vayiraṅ kuḻaittuṇṇu māvalitā ṉeṉṉum</l>
<l>vayira vaḻakkoḻittāy maṟṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You acquired the earth by means [of begging], not considering [it a big task].</l>
<l>Besides, [You] brought to an end the inimical ways</l>
<l>of the self-conceited Mahābalin who eats diamonds,</l>
<l rend="indent">melting [them] by [medicinal] means, oh!</l>
<l>Is there anything that will come out of such [acts for You]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
